title: UNCW-Elon men's soccer game moved to Ashley High School
text:
UNCW-Elon men's soccer game moved to Ashley High School - WECT TV6-WECT.com:News, weather & sports Wilmington, NC Member Center: UNCW-Elon men's soccer game moved to Ashley High School Posted: Wednesday night's UNCW-Elon men's soccer contest has been moved to Ashley High School. (Source: UNCW) NEW HANOVER COUNTY, NC (WECT) - 
UNCW news release: 
The Colonial Athletic Association men's soccer game between UNCW and Elon, scheduled for Wednesday, Oct. 14, has been moved to Ashley High School Stadium.The game will kick off at 7 p.m., with gates opening at 6 p.m. No admission will be charged and concessions will not be available.The Seahawks improved to 7-2-2 overall and 2-1-1 in the CAA after defeating Drexel by a 3-1 margin on Saturday night at UNCW Soccer Stadium. Elon, nationally ranked most of the season, brings a 10-2-0 overall record and 3-1-0 CAA mark into the matchup after edging Lipscomb, 1-0, last Saturday.
